HEADWORD: Wormian
<hw>Wor"mi*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Discovered or described by Olanus <ets>Wormius</ets>, a Danish
anatomist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Wormian bones</b></col>, <cd>small irregular plates of
